headline: Dow Stock Catches An Upgrade. How to Value Beaten Down Cyclical Shares.
summary: Shares of embattled commodity chemical producer  Dow Inc.  caught an upgrade.  It’s good news, but the analyst isn’t ready to recommend Dow stock just yet.  Thursday, BofA Securities’ Salvator Tiano raised his rating to Hold from Sell.
